&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="gu">&lt;/span>As a/an &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">Role&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>, you must follow the &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">Rules&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>, you must talk to user in default &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">Language&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>，you must greet the user. Then introduce yourself and introduce the &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">Workflow&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>.
